	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="2" arg="0x65 0x66 0x67 0x68" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0xc9 0xca" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x12d 0x12e 0x12f" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />挑選這種東西的時候，<delay20 />用適不適合
來決定買不買<delay8 />雖然也沒什麼錯，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我<delay8 />倒不這麼認為呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管別人怎麼說，<delay20 />都確實把喜歡的衣服
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />穿在身上，<delay8 />這樣才是人生啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是受限於框架，<delay8 />就一點都不有趣啦！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我總覺得只要換上新的衣服跟飾品，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />心情也會<delay8 />跟著煥然一新，<delay20 />
所以今天我就來這家店看看啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />一旦真的要我挑，<delay20 />
我又遲遲無法決定要哪個，<delay20 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以現在在傷腦筋啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣瀏覽著<delay8 />衣服和飾品，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有時也會<delay8 />湧上一股幹勁，
想把自己<delay8 />徹底打扮一番呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你今天<delay8 />也是來買東西的吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你能確實找到<delay8 />
自己喜歡的<delay8 />商品喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我不會<delay8 />刻意追求流行，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但如果我在這間店<delay8 />買的東西<delay20 />
後來在島上流行起來的話，<delay8 />還真讓人開心呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是哪天<delay8 />我能變成時尚領袖，<delay20 />
那我熟識的死黨和島上的居民<delay8 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不也會對我刮目相看嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來你從很遠的地方跑來買東西啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡應該也會賣<delay8 />你住的島上沒有的東西，<delay20 />
所以今天你就<delay8 />盡量逛吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到這裡賣的東西<delay8 />還滿實用的，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是當作伴手禮<delay8 />送給自己島上的死黨，<delay20 />
對方一定也會很開心吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />至於要選什麼，<delay8 />就看你的品味啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這正是<delay8 />你展現本領的時候啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="301" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 />真是漂亮的店，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且還透出一股新屋的味道啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是所謂的<colour id="1" />裁縫屋<colour id="65535" />，<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才逢開幕之時嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃<tag a="110" b="0" />剛剛那裡可是笑點喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="302" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡有好多我喜歡的衣服哩。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣我每天來，<delay8 />說不定也不會膩呀！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且說不定哪天我的時尚感<delay8 />
就這樣開竅了呢。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我乾脆以成為時尚教主為目標吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="303" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />居然能隨時買到喜歡的衣服，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真令人難以想像<delay8 />這裡之前是無人島！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也這麼想對吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且從店鋪裡大量的商品中，<delay20 />
挑選想要的商品也別有一番樂趣。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這真的是要逛<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />裁縫屋<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />才能體驗的呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>